
you get badges when you achieve the following:
   - first time you add a card
   - first time you create list
   - learn 100 words
   - learn 1000 words
   - learn 2000 words
   - learn 3000 words
   - learn 5000 words

get reputation when:
   - someone votes up your word list
   - someone uses your word list
   - you get a card right
   - each time you get a badge

